This swimming program takes an individualized approach and design for adults with physical, developmental or communicative disabilities who require specialized instruction in and around the water.  A one 2 one volunteer works with each adult under the guidance of a specialty swimming instructor. Aims: comfort in water, buoyancy and movement, submersion, surface support, front and back swims, shallow and deep water activities, water safety education.
